We are currently looking to recruit a Housekeeping Desk Coordinator to join our Housekeeping team. You will be responsible for attending and coordinating all telephone calls, guest request and operational request for the Housekeeping team.
In return we offer competitive pay and benefits, and a chance to work with a great team of talented people. Most importantly, we'll give you the Room to be yourself.
